<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SGMP · Extractor SIPOC</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #EEF3F9;
      --bg-2: #E7EEF7;
      --panel: #FFFFFF;
      --text: #0A1F44;
      --muted: #5B6F8A;
      --primary: #0B2E59;
      --primary-2: #1A56DB;
      --accent: #00C2FF;
      --accent-soft: rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.10);
      --ok: #27AE60;
      --warn: #F2994A;
      --danger: #C0392B;
      --line: rgba(11, 46, 89, 0.12);
      --shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(11, 46, 89, 0.10);
      --radius: 24px;
      --content-width: min(1520px, calc(100vw - 32px));
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 0%, rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.12), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 92% 10%, rgba(26, 86, 219, 0.10), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg), var(--bg-2));
    }

    button,
    input,
    textarea,
    select {
      font: inherit;
    }

    button {
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 13px;
      padding: 11px 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: 0.18s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(11, 46, 89, 0.13);
    }

    input,
    textarea,
    select {
      width: 100%;
      color: var(--text);
      background: #FFFFFF;
      border: 1px solid rgba(11, 46, 89, 0.14);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 11px 12px;
      outline: none;
    }

    textarea {
      min-height: 150px;
      resize: vertical;
      font-family: Consolas, "SFMono-Regular", monospace;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    input:focus,
    textarea:focus,
    select:focus {
      border-color: rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.55);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.12);
    }

    pre {
      max-height: 360px;
      overflow: auto;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
      color: #DDF5FF;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #071C36, #0B2E59);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.18);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .app {
      width: var(--content-width);
      margin: 14px auto 26px;
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 230px 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: stretch;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 11% 20%, rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.20), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #071C36 0%, #0B2E59 54%, #173F73 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(7, 28, 54, 0.22);
    }

    .express-agent {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 15%, rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.18), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04));
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.13),
        0 18px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    }

    .express-bot {
  position: relative;
  width: 132px;
  height: 142px;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
}

.express-glow {
  position: absolute;
  width: 118px;
  height: 118px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background:
    radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.30),
      rgba(26, 86, 219, 0.10) 56%,
      transparent 72%
    );
  filter: blur(1px);
}

.express-head {
  position: absolute;
  top: 8px;
  width: 96px;
  height: 78px;
  border-radius: 34px;
  background:
    radial-gradient(
      circle at 50% 10%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.30) 18%,
      transparent 32%
    ),
    linear-gradient(
      160deg,
      #F7FCFF 0%,
      #DDF5FF 48%,
      #9BE7FF 100%
    );
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
  box-shadow:
    0 16px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24),
    inset 0 -10px 18px rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.16);
  z-index: 3;
}

.express-head::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 16px;
  right: 16px;
  top: 23px;
  height: 30px;
  border-radius: 18px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #061C36, #0B2E59);
  box-shadow:
    inset 0 0 14px rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.30),
    0 0 16px rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.20);
}

.express-eye {
  position: absolute;
  top: 33px;
  width: 9px;
  height: 9px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #00C2FF;
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.95);
  z-index: 4;
}

.express-eye.left {
  left: 36px;
}

.express-eye.right {
  right: 36px;
}

.express-smile {
  position: absolute;
  left: 43px;
  top: 48px;
  width: 12px;
  height: 5px;
  border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
  border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.9);
  z-index: 4;
}

.express-body {
  position: absolute;
  top: 88px;
  width: 72px;
  height: 48px;
  border-radius: 24px 24px 28px 28px;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0B2E59, #1A56DB);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28);
  box-shadow:
    0 14px 26px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22),
    inset 0 0 18px rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.20);
  z-index: 2;
}

.express-core {
  position: absolute;
  left: 50%;
  top: 13px;
  width: 26px;
  height: 26px;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.65);
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle, #00C2FF 0 28%, transparent 31%),
    rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.10);
  box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.42);
}

.express-arm {
  position: absolute;
  top: 96px;
  width: 16px;
  height: 34px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1A56DB, #00C2FF);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24);
  z-index: 1;
}

.express-arm.left {
  left: 20px;
  transform: rotate(16deg);
}

.express-arm.right {
  right: 20px;
  transform: rotate(-16deg);
}


    .synapse-express-img {
      width: 138px;
      height: 138px;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 10px auto;
      filter:
        drop-shadow(0 14px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24))
        drop-shadow(0 0 18px rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.18));
    }

    .agent-name {
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .agent-sub {
      margin-top: 6px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.2vw, 2rem);
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      line-height: 1.5;
      max-width: 880px;
    }

    .hero-actions,
    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      color: #FFFFFF;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-2));
    }

    .btn-ok {
      color: #FFFFFF;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F766E, #27AE60);
    }

    .btn-warn {
      color: #FFFFFF;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D97706, #F2994A);
    }

    .btn-danger {
      color: #FFFFFF;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A93226, #C0392B);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      color: var(--primary);
      background: #FFFFFF;
      border: 1px solid rgba(11, 46, 89, 0.14);
    }

    .status-bar {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      border: 1px solid rgba(11, 46, 89, 0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .status-bar strong {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 16px;
      height: calc(100vh - 32px);
      overflow-y: auto;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        rgba(8, 34, 68, 0.98),
        rgba(11, 46, 89, 0.96) 42%,
        rgba(15, 58, 110, 0.94)
      );
      box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    }

    .sidebar h2 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .sidebar p {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: rgba(225, 244, 255, 0.78);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .step-list,
    .block-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .nav-item,
    .block-item {
      color: rgba(225, 244, 255, 0.88);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.115), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.045));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .nav-item.active,
    .block-item.active {
      color: #FFFFFF;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.36), rgba(26, 86, 219, 0.22) 50%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08));
      border-color: rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.62);
      border-left-color: #00C2FF;
    }

    .nav-item strong,
    .block-item strong {
      display: block;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .nav-item small,
    .block-item small {
      display: block;
      color: rgba(225, 244, 255, 0.78);
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .workspace {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .section-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-title h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.12rem;
    }

    .section-title p {
      margin: 4px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--primary);
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.20);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1.5fr;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .field {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .field label {
      color: #42617F;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .image-stage {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 420px;
      max-height: 72vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: auto;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(11, 46, 89, 0.22);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #F8FBFF;
    }

    .image-wrap {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
      line-height: 0;
    }

    .image-wrap img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .seg-box {
      position: absolute;
      line-height: 1.2;
      border: 2px dashed #00C2FF;
      background: rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.08);
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .seg-box.active {
      border-color: #F2994A;
      background: rgba(242, 153, 74, 0.14);
    }

    .seg-label {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      padding: 4px 6px;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      background: #0B2E59;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 0;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
    }


    .crop-toolbar {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px dashed rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.24);
    }

    .crop-status {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .segment-image-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .segment-image-actions button {
      padding: 9px 12px;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
    }

    .summary {
      max-height: 380px;
      overflow: auto;
      background: #F8FBFF;
      border: 1px solid rgba(11, 46, 89, 0.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .summary h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .summary h4 {
      margin: 12px 0 6px;
    }

    .summary ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .msg {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 11px 13px;
      border-radius: 13px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .msg.show {
      display: block;
    }

    .msg.ok {
      color: #176B3A;
      background: rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.10);
      border: 1px solid rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.22);
    }

    .msg.warn {
      color: #8A570D;
      background: rgba(242, 153, 74, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(242, 153, 74, 0.24);
    }

    .msg.err {
      color: #A93226;
      background: rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.10);
      border: 1px solid rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.22);
    }

    .mini-note {
      padding: 11px 12px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      color: #42617F;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      border: 1px dashed rgba(0, 194, 255, 0.24);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }


    .source-tools {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 190px 190px;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: end;
    }

    .hidden {
      display: none !important;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero,
      .layout,
      .grid-2,
      .grid-3,
      .source-tools {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .sidebar {
        position: relative;
        height: auto;
      }
    }
  </style>

<style id="sgmp-extractor-module-rules">
  /* SGMP: extractor como módulo independiente, sin avatar visible */
  .express-agent{display:none !important;}
  .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr !important;}
  .sgmp-ai-status{
    margin-top:14px;padding:12px 14px;border-radius:16px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.86);border:1px solid rgba(11,46,89,.10);
    color:#5B6F8A;font-size:.92rem;display:none;
  }
  .sgmp-ai-status.show{display:block;}
  .sgmp-ai-status strong{color:#0B2E59;}
  .sgmp-ai-loader{
    margin-top:10px;height:12px;border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden;
    background:rgba(11,46,89,.10);border:1px solid rgba(11,46,89,.08);
  }
  .sgmp-ai-loader span{
    display:block;width:42%;height:100%;border-radius:999px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#FFFFFF,#00C2FF,#1A56DB,#FFFFFF);
    background-size:220% 100%;animation:sgmpAiLoading 1.15s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes sgmpAiLoading{
    0%{transform:translateX(-120%);background-position:0% 50%;}
    100%{transform:translateX(260%);background-position:100% 50%;}
  }
  .sgmp-manual-hint{
    margin-top:10px;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:14px;
    background:rgba(242,153,74,.12);border:1px dashed rgba(242,153,74,.30);
    color:#8A570D;font-size:.86rem;line-height:1.45;display:none;
  }
  .sgmp-manual-hint.show{display:block;}
</style>

</head>

<body>
  <div class="app">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="express-agent">
        <!-- Robot visual liviano. Para versión final puede reemplazarse por:
        <img class="synapse-express-img" src="data:image/png;base64,AQUI_BASE64_FINAL" alt="Synapse Express" />
        -->
        <div class="express-bot" aria-label="Synapse Express">
          <div class="express-glow"></div>
          <div class="express-head">
            <span class="express-eye left"></span>
            <span class="express-eye right"></span>
            <span class="express-smile"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="express-body">
            <span class="express-core"></span>
          </div>
          <span class="express-arm left"></span>
          <span class="express-arm right"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-name">EXTRACTOR SIPOC</div>
        <div class="agent-sub">Módulo SGMP</div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-content">
        <div>
          <h1>Extractor SIPOC</h1>
          <p>
            Herramienta independiente para leer el cuerpo visual de un SIPOC preparado, extraer lógica funcional por segmentos,
            incorporar notas aclaratorias pegadas como texto plano y generar un JSON compacto compatible con el LMP.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <button class="btn" onclick="openLmpModule()" type="button">Abrir LMP</button>
          <button class="btn-ghost" onclick="saveSession()" type="button">Guardar sesión local</button>
          <button class="btn-ghost" onclick="loadSession()" type="button">Cargar sesión local</button>
          <input id="backupImportInput" class="hidden" type="file" accept="application/json,.json" onchange="importBackupJson(event)" />
          <button class="btn-ghost" onclick="triggerBackupImport()" type="button">Cargar respaldo JSON</button>
          <button class="btn-ok" onclick="exportBackupJson()" type="button">Descargar respaldo JSON</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="status-bar">
      <strong>Regla operativa:</strong> el Extractor no analiza, no propone y no inventa. Solo extrae la lógica visible del SIPOC y consolida notas aclaratorias pegadas manualmente.
    </div>

    <div id="sgmpAiStatus" class="sgmp-ai-status"></div>

    <div class="layout">
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <h2>Flujo de trabajo</h2>
        <p>Trabaja en orden: imagen SIPOC, segmentación, extracción por segmento, notas aclaratorias y consolidación LMP.</p>

        <div class="step-list">
          <div class="nav-item active" data-step="source" onclick="showStep('source')">
            <strong>1. Imagen SIPOC</strong>
            <small>Cuerpo visual preparado</small>
          </div>

          <div class="nav-item" data-step="segmentation" onclick="showStep('segmentation')">
            <strong>2. Segmentación</strong>
            <small>Prompt estándar + JSON</small>
          </div>

          <div class="nav-item" data-step="extraction" onclick="showStep('extraction')">
            <strong>3. Extracción</strong>
            <small>Lógica por segmento</small>
          </div>

          <div class="nav-item" data-step="notes" onclick="showStep('notes')">
            <strong>4. Notas aclaratorias</strong>
            <small>Texto plano manual</small>
          </div>

          <div class="nav-item" data-step="final" onclick="showStep('final')">
            <strong>5. Consolidación</strong>
            <small>Prompt + JSON LMP</small>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr style="border:0;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);margin:16px 0" />

        <h2>Segmentos</h2>
        <div id="segmentList" class="block-list"></div>
      </aside>

      <main class="workspace">
        <section id="step_source" class="card">
          <div class="section-title">
            <div>
              <h2>Imagen preparada del SIPOC</h2>
              <p>
                Sube únicamente el cuerpo visual del SIPOC: proveedores, entradas, carriles, actividades, decisiones, salidas y clientes.
                No incluyas encabezado superior ni notas aclaratorias.
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="pill">Imagen</span>
          </div>

          <div class="mini-note">
            El encabezado del proceso se conserva en el LMP. Las notas aclaratorias se pegarán luego como texto plano. Esta herramienta solo procesa la lógica funcional visible.
          </div>

          <div class="field" style="margin-top:12px">
